Ecuador's indigenous communities hold traditional knowledge of natural
medicines and therapeutic use of plants. [This documentary by iosphera
](http://vimeo.com/17556813)shows the importance of preserving this knowledge
from biopiracy for the future of these communities. (via
[cinealoido](http://log.cinealoido.com/post/13305188871/salud-verde-salud-
indigena-en-ecuador-by))

